## Review Notes

- **Wrapper contract:** `TxLoadingState` locks `variant="loading"`; pass `loading` only when the base spinner illustration should replace the default loading illustration.
- **Recommendation:** Use `TxLoadingState` for full-panel first-load states; use `TxSpinner` or `TxProgressBar loading` for inline/local waiting.
- **Accessibility:** Loading copy should name what is being loaded, for example “Loading rules”, not only “Loading”.
